It is then possible to do any number of things with the data such as...

Most popular event:

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
me %>% 
  count(event) %>% 
  arrange(-n) %>% 
  head(5) %>% 
  gt() %>% 
  cols_label(
    n = "Number of performances",
    event = "Event"
  )
```

